{"tid":1399783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行人士、示威者注意","createTime":"2019-08-03T09:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T09:53:45.000Z","uid":55597,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8c82dd442d07f9402489b82e22550ff760650b5","tid":1399783,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:46:12.000Z","msg":"今日遊行冇警察，如果出事就入晒你地數<br />\n已有 post 發現有警察換黑衫，可能會混入人群扮示威者，再搞事<br />\n<br />\n所以大家一定要克制，甚至離開現場"},{"pid":"21f67d70272adbc0c4b4f84d40192e038a9793e9","tid":1399783,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:47:20.000Z","msg":"人多好重要，唔好散住，街坊look去文化中心行下先"},{"pid":"ad05491d157f75f7d5c101d6075256bfa4895f42","tid":1399783,"uid":82588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:48:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5efbf151c828a40b74df95fdb34f846e1d3fe8bb","tid":1399783,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fc7ac8ee34e2da59c12bc2d187f0a19fdd1442","tid":1399783,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"[有圖] 警車上警已換黑衫帶上口罩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1399747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1399747</a>"},{"pid":"83d60b5437252c9c16af9987d3c5a016b3d32311","tid":1399783,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:53:30.000Z","msg":"唔係叫大家散，亦都冇資格叫大家散<br />\n係要小心，今日真係會有鬼<br />\n要留意啲形跡可疑，不斷影相<br />\n或者無故想引發衝擊行為嘅人<br />\n今次遊行示威應該唔需要衝擊<br />\n保持住冇警察就冇衝擊嘅狀態<br />\n等市民將衝擊現象同警察出現掛鉤"},{"pid":"25d2d557b5fd7e115f86ada8e0c4a306eee964d9","tid":1399783,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5fc7ac8ee34e2da59c12bc2d187f0a19fdd1442","tid":1399783,"uid":235465